{"tid":1460764,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"聲援811義士 今日下午九龍城提堂","createTime":"2019-08-13T04:46:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T05:11:22.000Z","uid":61672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3422f0cbbde7485dacb9e299123bc86c2e26f268","tid":1460764,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:46:18.000Z","msg":"【8月11日血腥鎮壓 17名義士下午提堂】<br />\n<br />\n17名在811鎮壓中被捕義士將於今日下午在九龍城裁判法院提堂，提堂時間及相關控罪正待警方確實。<br />\n<br />\n港共政權及黑警對義士逼害不斷升級，濫捕濫告之餘，在811當日更採取血腥鎮壓。各媒體直播時已證明黑警對被捕義士及香港市民採取不必要武力，多名義士被黑警扣押後，身體更多處受傷。<br />\n<br />\n星火同盟懇請各同道下午到庭聲援，支持眾被捕義士，令他們知道各方並無因為血腥鎮壓而退縮。"},{"pid":"689be84ff0d1b5ea016611d024050abf3293f17f","tid":1460764,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:46:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46d1d3d5e61f9b58462030e1a9227edf9f6fa93f","tid":1460764,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:46:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65d4faa31c9bddbd51d7fceb45912dc0a969fc27","tid":1460764,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:46:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb1777f1300ae0387a1eac20b69aacfc880abe5b","tid":1460764,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:47:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"561eb4e6e6545c1072949c99c19f601d76b88976","tid":1460764,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:47:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c55a99f20fff59d7acb6ea4fd40dc70a75950146","tid":1460764,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:47:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7b53ac7ecef753b1168dd2450a77ff174b298252","tid":1460764,"uid":47905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:47:23.000Z","msg":"推 去完入機場"},{"pid":"ed8cb3df067e4cd5cfe49a52dbd79718d6cce450","tid":1460764,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:47:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f1b431895a72e6bd50